c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Figma AI and Tome share a solid foundation of core features including Templates, Drag And Drop, Brand Kit, Ai Generation. Where Figma AI pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Tome uniquely offers Stock Assets, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Figma AI holds an overall score of 9/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Tome scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Figma AI and Tome offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Figma AI's free tier and Tome's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
